{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0112swz2uJ3s4yByn5zgLrMp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WHRWEWaPyaCZPXKYMyqGFY","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"- No observability gaps reported by verifier for this story.","new_string":"- No observability gaps reported by verifier for this story.\n\n### 8-5-rust-dockerfile-template — create-story (2026-03-23T10:41Z)\n\n- **Pre-existing stub overwritten:** Stub story file already existed from earlier epic planning. Overwritten with comprehensive version.\n- **Workflow naming mismatch:** workflow.md referenced in skill was actually workflow.yaml — minor.\n- **Risk: checkNoSourceCopy validator false positive:** The `COPY src/` pattern in the validator regex could false-match on Rust template's `COPY . .` builder stage. Story documents this prominently but dev agent could miss it.\n- **Risk: AC7 integration-required:** Depends on `detectStack()` returning `'rust'` for real Rust project during `codeharness init`. Cannot verify purely via unit tests."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1998,"cache_read_input_tokens":41278,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1998},"output_tokens":55,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"daf25720-e009-4a3c-8a3c-df9d68d99484","uuid":"93ea7d2c-d33d-420f-be6d-3b79485a7658"}
