{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01N2qjWGs1ch85to3kXHK7E1","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Story 8.5: Rust Dockerfile Template Generation — Verification Proof\n     2→\n     3→Verified: 2026-03-23\n     4→Verifier: Claude Opus 4.6 (black-box, no source access)\n     5→Container: codeharness-verify (codeharness v0.23.1)\n     6→\n     7→---\n     8→\n     9→## AC1: Rust stack returns `stack: 'rust'` (not `'generic'`)\n    10→\n    11→```bash\n    12→docker exec codeharness-verify bash -c 'mkdir -p /tmp/rust-test && cd /tmp/rust-test && cat > Cargo.toml << EOF\n    13→[package]\n    14→name = \"myapp\"\n    15→version = \"0.1.0\"\n    16→edition = \"2021\"\n    17→EOF\n    18→codeharness init --json 2>&1'\n    19→```\n    20→\n    21→```output\n    22→{\"status\":\"fail\",\"stack\":\"rust\",\"enforcement\":{\"frontend\":true,\"database\":true,\"api\":true},\"documentation\":{\"agents_md\":\"skipped\",\"docs_scaffold\":\"skipped\",\"readme\":\"skipped\"},\"app_type\":\"generic\",\"dockerfile\":{\"generated\":true,\"stack\":\"rust\"},\"error\":\"Docker not installed\",\"docker\":{\"compose_file\":\"\",\"stack_running\":false,\"services\":[],\"ports\":{\"logs\":9428,\"metrics\":8428,\"traces\":16686,\"otel_grpc\":4317,\"otel_http\":4318}}}\n    23→```\n    24→\n    25→Key evidence: `\"dockerfile\":{\"generated\":true,\"stack\":\"rust\"}` — stack is `\"rust\"`, NOT `\"generic\"`.\n    26→\n    27→[OBSERVABILITY GAP] No log events detected for this user interaction\n    28→\n    29→**Verdict: PASS**\n    30→\n    31→---\n    32→\n    33→## AC2: Multi-stage build with `FROM rust:1.82-slim AS builder` and `FROM debian:bookworm-slim`\n    34→\n    35→```bash\n    36→docker exec codeharness-verify cat /tmp/rust-test/Dockerfile\n    37→```\n    38→\n    39→```output\n    40→# === Builder stage ===\n    41→FROM rust:1.82-slim AS builder\n    42→\n    43→WORKDIR /build\n    44→\n    45→# Copy project files\n    46→COPY . .\n    47→